value.0: A disgusting eyeball severed from the vilest of Underdark's beholders is grafted into this horrid stone portal - and it looks to be very much alive. There is no telling who, or what, created this unsettling object.

A Monument to the ancient Sith Lord Naga Sadow. Within the depths of the mystic flames you can make out the shape of a great blade implanted within a pedestal, forever beyond your reach..
